snippet.title: My Little Pony Rainbow Runners | Google Play Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download on the Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.budgestudios.googleplay.MyLittlePonyRainbowRunners


Run, jump, fly and restore the colors of the world with all your favorite ponies!

A powerful color-stealing spell has been unleashed on Ponyville and it’s up to your favorite ponies to break it with the power of Friendship. Run, jump, awaken your ponies’ Rainbow Powers and use their epic abilities to bring the colors back to the world!

Like us on Facebook! www.facebook.com/budgestudios
